user_data.general_preference: I generally prefer clothing items that are comfortable, well-fitting, and practical. I value soft fabrics with a good amount of stretch, as well as features that enhance comfort, such as moisture-wicking and wrinkle resistance. I appreciate items that can be dressed up or down, allowing for versatility in my wardrobe. On the other hand, I dislike items that do not fit as expected, particularly when sizing is inconsistent, as this can lead to frustration. I also prefer not to deal with complicated or uncomfortable designs, and I am less inclined to purchase items that do not meet my expectations for quality and comfort.
